==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /pəˈteɪtəʊ/

===Etymology===
From Taino [[batata]] via Spanish [[patata]].

===Noun===
'''potato''' (plural: '''[[potatoes]]''')

#A plant [[tuber]] often eaten as a starchy vegetable, particularly in the [[Americas]] and [[Europe]]. 

